        <span class="nx">utilization_threshold</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">Optional[str]</span> = None<span class="p">) -&gt;</span> AutoscalingConfig</code></pre></div>

{{% choosable language csharp %}}
<dl class="resources-properties"><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="state_clusterid_csharp">
<a href="#state_clusterid_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Cluster<wbr>Id</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The id of kubernetes cluster.
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="state_cooldownduration_csharp">
<a href="#state_cooldownduration_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Cool<wbr>Down<wbr>Duration</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The cool down duration. Default is `10m`. If the delay (cooldown) value is set too long, there could be complaints that the Horizontal Pod Autoscaler is not responsive to workload changes. However, if the delay value is set too short, the scale of the replicas set may keep thrashing as usual.
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="state_gpuutilizationthreshold_csharp">
<a href="#state_gpuutilizationthreshold_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Gpu<wbr>Utilization<wbr>Threshold</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The scale-in threshold for GPU instance. Default is `0.5`.
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="state_scaninterval_csharp">
<a href="#state_scaninterval_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Scan<wbr>Interval</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
